Title: Relates to the misbranding of food products not containing meat
Summary: Relates to the misbranding of food products not containing meat; establishes a food product shall be deemed to be misbranded if the food product is labeled or branded in a false, deceptive or misleading manner that misrepresents the product as meat, meat food product or poultry.
LawCode: Add ยง201-j, Ag & Mkts L
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the agriculture and markets law, in relation to the misbranding of food products not containing meat
